    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi @ValdoGhafoor,\r\n\r\nThe cache for `ais-infinite-hits` is separate and we do not provide a way to invalidate it.\r\n\r\nHowever there is a `cache` prop so you can provide your own, you can make a custom cache that can be invalidated like I made here : https://codesandbox.io/s/twilight-voice-d5zuj6?file=/src/App.vue (I wanted to import `isEqual` from `instantsearch.js` but it doesn't seem to work so I copy/pasted it :/ )\r\n\r\nYou can then call `cache.invalidate` inside `refresh` or whenever you want to.",
